     					<h4>Priority Order Explanation</h4>
     					<p>
     					    As the child’s age increases the Skills that had a higher priority first will have a lower priority after because he/she should have already gained those skills at an early age. <br/>
     					    If the teacher believe a child needs special support in any particular area, teachers should send a message to his/her parents, giving some suggestions as to how to address that problem.
     					</p>
